welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Lakeland South! Get ready to experience the charm and beauty of our city, known for its stunning lakes and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Lakeland South has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at SEA serves both domestic and international flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at SEA is primarily used for domestic flights and offers a modern and efficient travel experience.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at SEA serves international and some domestic flights and features a variety of dining and shopping options for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport. Connect to the network and follow the prompts to access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport serves domestic and international flights. It features modern amenities and services for travelers.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport is equipped to handle a variety of goods and packages, ensuring efficient and timely delivery.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Industrial Airport caters to the needs of private and charter flights, offering VIP services and exclusive amenities.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy complimentary WiFi throughout the airport. Premium high-speed WiFi is also available for purchase.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is primarily used for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a login is required.
